description:
This is a 36 minute workout called '30 min FULL BODY STRENGTH WORKOUT | With Dumbbells (And Without) | No Repeats' from the channel fitbymik.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging and Moderate.
